{"tid":1398511,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[即興西藏] 流浪在拉薩街頭，我是世間最美的情郎","createTime":"2019-08-02T22:08:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T08:00:08.000Z","uid":157925,"like":14,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2e6ef925d6051924b723c9f21ca322b8530ca235","tid":1398511,"uid":157925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T22:08:46.000Z","msg":"住進布達拉宮，我是雪域最大的王。<br />\n流浪在拉薩街頭，我是世間最美的情郎。<br />\n<br />\n戴頂個頭盔先，本人一向反共，出發前仲成日去發夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上年去色達既時候，當地朋友同我講過倉央嘉措的故仔，自此就對藏族文化有左興趣。呢首詩係佢當年做達賴喇嘛時作既。簡單就講佢做左達賴之後仲好掛住以前既情人，最後引來政變令到佢比人趕走左仲命都冇埋（一說話係逃走左）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CJpXpE1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCJpXpE1.png&h=5f35b4c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n補番張去年色達影既相，咁岩手機得番呢一張風景相，其他有樣既就唔post啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事緣係咁，原本打算去成都搵女女玩（咁岩佢去果到做一排野），點知可能太耐冇見又本身感情淡曬，所以一落機就人係咁鬧我曬佢時間搞到佢冇得去街咁。咁當然我地大家以前都有好多問題冇解決啦。詳情唔多講，最後就係機場大鬧一番就好絕情咁分手收場啦。<br />\n<br />\n一個人要頂十日以上真係怕悶，成都又去過幾次，所以最後就即興去西藏。原本有諗過坐火車去，點知得番硬座去西寧先再轉到車去拉薩，硬座十五粒鐘真係傻的嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後比貴少少錢買機票去西藏<br />\n提一提各位巴絲，香港人買機票都好煩下，因為唔係好多支網都比人用歡樂卡買去拉薩既機票。支牆又搞到上網好貴，搞左半日先買到<br />\n<br />\n事前冇咩準備，尋日都係買多一件風褸<br />\n希望一切順利啦<br />\n呢家出發，凌晨機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QptxdA5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQptxdA5.png&h=97b60dc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有冇巴絲又係拉薩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後入藏前都要講番句：<br />\n<br />\n「光復香港，時代革命！」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5c170f036b359cc5f6b79db3c6e15b2d9c71e4d","tid":1398511,"uid":164770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T22:11:04.000Z","msg":"下次坐硬座啦"},{"pid":"0f0fcef2ca4c53e952c3a6c2cf53fdb5c8238c7c","tid":1398511,"uid":157925,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a5c170f036b359cc5f6b79db3c6e15b2d9c71e4d","tid":1398511,"uid":164770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T22:11:04.000Z","msg":"下次坐硬座啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T22:16:02.000Z","msg":"坐高鐵五粒鐘都頂唔順啦<br />\n如果仲要係好慢既火車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06455fa920cd344c9965089da332a2c5c60e08e2","tid":1398511,"uid":157925,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T22:21:21.000Z","msg":"邊個又偷偷比負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有正評先有繼續post既動力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1df4746820e0ac09cca3f84b2cfa0b88f8eb4721","tid":1398511,"uid":157925,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T01:58:52.000Z","msg":"已到拉薩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ajDpQud.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FajDpQud.png&h=78597530&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"13c113377f001c6fed5a2bd5748a1eb8d2fdd7ff","tid":1398511,"uid":230215,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:20:53.000Z","msg":"西藏真係好撚靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a109b3a7773947e602234d6a383e54c829f6cdd","tid":1398511,"uid":157925,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"13c113377f001c6fed5a2bd5748a1eb8d2fdd7ff","tid":1398511,"uid":230215,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:20:53.000Z","msg":"西藏真係好撚靚<img src=\"/assets/face