eplyTime":"2019-08-03T02:20:53.000Z","msg":"西藏真係好撚靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:28:29.000Z","msg":"比個正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:33:00.000Z","msg":"有靚相先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當年納木錯過夜好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n珠峰大本營好似封左冇得再去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:51:52.000Z","msg":"影多幾張相post 上來"},{"pid":"b508f6063d0ab4e5cede3a495cf19bacdab8f5e8","tid":1398511,"uid":230215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:05:56.000Z","msg":"都成7~8年前同屋企人<br />\n前半大陸團好撚ON9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 後半自由行就好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果唔介意夾大陸人 你可以係拉薩去D旅館同人組隊併車<br />\n<br />\n納木錯建議留夜 跟團去到影人頭就冇時間要走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n後半自由行就決定要上去第2次 +過夜先有時間慢慢影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(雖然都仲係覺得唔夠時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"4e5f0fa990b5ad8aa500999434462bba22cfac5a","tid":1398511,"uid":157925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:48:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3soQMDX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3soQMDX.png&h=75a50a16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1147<br />\n拉薩街頭，有點冷<br />\n真係成條街都係紅色宣傳標語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3096acd49469de208b93dbe5abd89fd4b5d7f9a","tid":1398511,"uid":157925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:50:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SQixfx7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSQixfx7.png&h=4ec516c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n哇過馬路真係搵命博<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ba7e6b8448bea2938262224a9bf7aa2316f62f8","tid":1398511,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T04:51:44.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"3fff1232a6b36b748bd86358295eb3199ecccf42","tid":1398511,"uid":157925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T05:10:20.000Z","msg":"呢家係觀景餐廳食飯先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bkYYbxZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbkYYbxZ.png&h=54044b0d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a7a7a0ac7fd68b4c7a6594c51b43ef821d2df111","tid":1398511,"uid":157925,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3fff1232a6b36b748bd86358295eb3199ecccf42","tid":1398511,"uid":157925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T05:10:20.000Z","msg":"呢家係觀景餐廳食飯先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bkYYbxZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbkYYbxZ.png&h=54044b0d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T05:14:31.000Z","msg":"要去美團先用到歡樂卡買票，飛豬係買唔到既<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比人炒到要528人仔，真係貴到hihi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z9dpRyC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz9dpRyC.png&h=0312d1ae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b7a868122f63efc68ac1a17871fcd9ee587838f","tid":1398511,"uid":79023,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T05:24:36.000Z","msg":"仲番去俾支那人賺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去印度Sikkim, Bhutan, Nepal upper mustang都有得睇Tibetan culture啦，係都要去支那人控制既地方旅遊，仲話自己有發夢<br />\n收撚皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5deddb22e022855cb7341f8e7bdbc4ca203f7aa","tid":1398511,"uid":58116,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T05:30:35.000Z","msg":"收撚皮啦<br />\n依個時勢仲去支那<br />\n仲咁撚厚面皮講光復香港，時間革命<br />\n食撚屎啦，你依世留係拉薩唔好番香港"},{"pid":"772d4c5e5b0b8036349472becc3dc2b30265d576","tid":1398511,"uid":92492,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:11:59.000Z","msg":"支持樓主<br />\n咁係咪大家一世唔返大陸先"},{"pid":"34c9b549de7162decbb4fd8bf56737d558081c77","tid":1398511,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b7a868122f63efc68ac1a17871fcd9ee587838f","tid":1398511,"uid":79023,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T05:24:36.000Z","msg":"仲番去俾支那人賺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去印度Sikkim, Bhutan, Nepal upper mustang都有得睇Tibetan culture啦，係都要去支那人控制既地方旅遊，仲話自己有發夢<br />\n收撚皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:37:59.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"9e59ed380ee50f4aa581112d7ad2e014199b8a38","tid":1398511,"uid":58116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"772d4c5e5b0b8036349472becc3dc2b30265d576","tid":1398511,"uid":92492,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:11:59.000Z","msg":"支持樓主<br />\n咁係咪大家一世唔返大陸先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:50:24.000Z","msg":"唔係唔畀人去支那，只不過唔好又講自己成日去發夢，又話自己反共，又話光復香港咁啦，好撚噁心呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要係連登開post，收撚皮啦"},{"pid":"dde302a350744e89f3f84f77b269920ddde474cb","tid":1398511,"uid":157925,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:51:26.000Z","msg":"布達拉宮真係好靚<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p2ZXsZ0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp2ZXsZ0.png&h=ce977fe5&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}